## 1. Set-up:

\(a\) Convert these data from the individual-level format to the “person-period” format (i.e.,from wide to long).

```{r}
#1. 
head(data)

library(tidyverse)

data_long <- data %>%
  pivot_longer(
    cols = HamD0:HamD5,
    names_to = "time",
    values_to = "HamD"
  ) %>%
  mutate(
    time = as.numeric(gsub("HamD", "", time))
  ) %>%
  arrange(id, time)

head(data_long)
```

